---

<Layout title="首頁" description="歡迎來到 Ian's Blog，分享前端開發經驗、技術見解和個人成長的地方。">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center py-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        歡迎來到我的
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          技術博客
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        分享前端開發經驗、技術見解和個人成長的地方。
        使用 Astro + React + MDX + TypeScript 打造的現代博客。
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          瀏覽博客
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
          關於我
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tech Stack -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
        技術棧
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Astro</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">現代靜態網站生成器</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">⚛️</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">React</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">動態 UI 組件</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📝</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">MDX</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Markdown + JSX</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎨</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Tailwind</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">實用的 CSS 框架</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Featured Articles Section -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          精選文章
        </h2>
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
          查看全部
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- Article 1 -->
        <article class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold text-center px-4">
                歡迎來到我的博客
              </h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
              <span class="capitalize font-medium">技術</span>
              <span>•</span>
              <time>2024年5月24日</time>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              這是我的第一篇博客文章，介紹這個博客的技術架構和我的寫作計劃。
              使用 Astro、React、TypeScript 和 Tailwind CSS 打造。
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs rounded-full">Astro</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs rounded-full">React</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs rounded-full">TypeScript</span>
            </div>
            
            <a 
              href="/blog/welcome"
              class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium"
            >
              閱讀文章 →
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 2 -->
        <article class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-blue-600 relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold text-center px-4">
                現代前端開發工具鏈
              </h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">
              <span class="capitalize font-medium">教學</span>
              <span>•</span>
              <time>2024年5月25日</time>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              探討現代前端開發中必備的工具鏈，包括建構工具、包管理器、
              開發環境配置等實用指南。
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs rounded-full">Vite</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs rounded-full">ESBuild</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs rounded-full">工具鏈</span>
            </div>
            
            <a 
              href="/blog/modern-frontend-toolchain"
              class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium"
            >
              閱讀文章 →
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6">
            I
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            關於我
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            我是 Ian，一名熱愛前端開發的工程師。專精於 React、TypeScript 和現代 Web 技術。
            喜歡分享技術知識和探索新的開發工具，致力於創造優秀的用戶體驗。
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
            <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">GitHub</a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">Twitter</a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="/about" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">了解更多</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Newsletter Section -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">訂閱我的博客</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 opacity-90">
          定期收到最新的技術文章和開發心得，不錯過任何精彩內容。
        </p>
        <form class="max-w-md mx-auto flex gap-2">
          <input 
            type="email" 
            placeholder="輸入您的電子郵件"
            class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-gray-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-300"
            required
          >
          <button 
            type="submit"
            class="px-6 py-2 bg-white text-blue-600 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >
            訂閱
          </button>
        </form>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-75 mt-3">
          我們重視您的隱私，不會發送垃圾郵件。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .line-clamp-3 {
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Newsletter subscription handling
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const newsletterForm = document.querySelector('section form');
    
    if (newsletterForm) {
      newsletterForm.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const email = this.querySelector('input[type="email"]').value;
        
        if (email) {
          alert('感謝訂閱！我們會將最新文章發送到您的信箱。');
          this.querySelector('input[type="email"]').value = '';
        }
      });
    }
  });
</script>